  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On May 1, 2026 at 06:04 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                            <li>\n                                                        \n                                                            \n                                                                Read by \n                                                            \n                                                            100 Professionals\n                                                        \n                                                    </li>\n                                                                                    </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>New Delhi: Corporate hospital chian, <a href=\"/tag/fortis+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fortis Healthcare</a> is all set to host a two day internal conference in the national capital, to discuss future of <a href=\"/tag/cancer+care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cancer care</a>.Centred around the theme ‘Beyond <a href=\"/tag/evidence-based+oncology\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Evidence-Based Oncology</a>’, the summit will focus on sharing real world insights, outline newer innovations and strategies to integrate them in daily practices to improve outcomes.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The summit will see participation from over 50 cancer centers across India, along with 500 national and more than 100 international faculty from 25 countries.Over 25 thematic sessions,, it will feature renowned global experts across multiple oncology disciplines, including Proton therapy, MR - guided radiotherapy (MR Linac), radiation oncology, medical oncology, surgical oncology, hematology, pediatric hematology, gynae oncology and genomics</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>“The future of <a href=\"/tag/cancer+care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cancer care</a> lies in collaboration, innovation, and the ability to adapt evidence into personalized patient care pathways. Through the Fortis Cancer Summit, we are creating an ecosystem where clinicians, researchers, can exchange insights, challenge conventional approaches, and explore the next frontier of <a href=\"/tag/cancer+management\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cancer management</a>,” said Dr Nitesh Rohatgi, Principal Director, Medical Oncology, Fortis Memorial Research Institute, Gurugram.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>“By bringing together some of the finest oncology minds from across the globe, we aim to foster meaningful dialogue around advancing standards of care, improving access to <a href=\"/tag/cutting-edge+therapies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cutting-edge therapies</a>, and strengthening collaborative approaches that ultimately translate into better survival and quality of life for patients.” Dr Ankur Bahl, Principal Director, Medical Oncology, Fortis Memorial Research Institute, added.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On May 1, 2026 at 06:04 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On May 1, 2026 at 06:04 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferre